          "linkId": "final-diagnosis",
          "text": "Final diagnosis",
          "answer": [
            {
              "valueString": "Right colon, right hemicolectomy: Moderately differentiated adenocarcinoma, invading through muscularis propria into pericolonic fat (pT3). Metastatic carcinoma in 1 of 18 regional lymph nodes (pN1a). All surgical margins are negative."
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "linkId": "additional-comments",
          "text": "Additional comments",
          "answer": [
            {
              "valueString": "Recommend molecular testing for mismatch repair (MMR) protein expression by immunohistochemistry and KRAS/NRAS/BRAF mutation analysis to guide adjuvant therapy."
            }
